# Original Birman source files (not redistributed). Patterns are anchored
# on "Ilya Birman" in the middle so they only match upstream filenames at
# repo root, not our own generated `Polish – Kirkouski Typographic.icns`
# inside `assets/icons/`. The previous generic `Russian *.icns` rule ate
# the Russian variant of our bundle icon and broke the v0.3 release build.
# The leading `/` anchors to repo root so the rule never reaches into
# subdirectories. Glob middle-bit covers both U+2013 EN DASH and the
# cp1252-mangled form some unzip tools produce.
/English *Ilya Birman*.keylayout
/English *Ilya Birman*.icns
/Russian *Ilya Birman*.keylayout
/Russian *Ilya Birman*.icns

# Frontend
web/node_modules/
web/dist/

